trans-unit.source: BlockCollection defines the allowable child content of the <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument"></xref>, <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.Section"></xref>, <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.ListItem"></xref>, <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.TableCell"></xref>, <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.Floater"></xref>, and <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.Figure"></xref> elements.
trans-unit.target: BlockCollection 정의의 콘텐츠는 사용할 수 있는 자식은 <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument"> </xref>, <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.Section"> </xref>, <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.ListItem"> </xref>, <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.TableCell"> </xref>, <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.Floater"> </xref>, 및 <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.Figure"> </xref> 요소입니다.

trans-unit.source: BlockCollection creation is only permitted inside an element that owns a BlockCollection, such as a <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument> or <xref:System.Windows.Documents.TextElement>.
trans-unit.target: BlockCollection 생성은 같은 <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument>나 <xref:System.Windows.Documents.TextElement>.</xref:System.Windows.Documents.TextElement> </xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument> BlockCollection를 소유 하는 요소 내 에서만 허용 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: As such, a BlockCollection cannot be instantiated directly and has no default or overloaded constructor.
trans-unit.target: 따라서 한 BlockCollection 직접 인스턴스화할 수 없습니다 및 기본값이 없는 또는 오버 로드 된 생성자입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the first <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.Block"></xref> element within this instance of <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.BlockCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 첫 번째 <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.Block"> </xref> 의이 인스턴스 내에서 요소 <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.BlockCollection"> </xref>합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the last <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.Block"></xref> element within this instance of <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.BlockCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 기간의 가져옵니다 <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.Block"> </xref> 의이 인스턴스 내에서 요소 <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.BlockCollection"> </xref>합니다.
